Folder meanings
________________________________________________________________

index.php

  Entry point to the application, just includes the main.php file into
  the server/ folder

server/

  Server side code

client/

  Client side code

images/

  Static images used into the application

style/

  Style sheets

data/

  Data files used by the server side code to store the application
  state. The position of this files can be configurated by the
  configuration.php file into the server/ folder. The web server has
  to create and modify files under this directory, so it should have
  the ownership on all this filesystem branch.
